Rating: NC-17<br>
Category: Angst/Romance (in a really sick &amp; twisted way)/Smut/Supernatural (eh – sort of) – Chloe/Lex, but there are some other pairings along the way.<br>
Spoilers: Anything through the end of the second season is fair game.<br>
Summary: A local microbrewery starts using meteor rocks to process their beer, giving it a kick that makes the people who drink it think that they’re dreaming and then act accordingly.<br>
